law.catch_line: Provisions of KRS 365.800 to 365.840 not waivable.
law.text: The provisions of KRS 365.800 to 365.840 shall represent a public policy of this Commonwealth and shall not be waivable in any retail agreement contract, and any attempted waiver shall be void.
law.history: Amended 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 125, sec. 3, effective June 25, 2013. -- Created 2004 Ky. Acts ch. 144, sec. 13, effective April 21, 2004.
